title: Donation by Royal Bank of Canada to support student entrepreneurs (University of Windsor)
text: ( Source : University of Windsor ) An $800, 000 donation by the Royal Bank of Canada Foundation , announced Tuesday, will support programs in the Entrepreneurship Practice and Innovation Centre (EPICentre) to help students and recent graduates
